title: Did Newly Elected Virginia Democrat Joe Morrissey in the Past Have Sex with His Teenage Receptionist?
subtitle: Despite a long and winding history of scandal, Joe Morrissey was elected to the Virginia State Senate in the fall of 2019.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: Joe Morrissey, a Democrat, was elected to the Virginia State Senate even though he had sex with his teenage receptionist and has been disbarred.
